<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 04 at 3:19AM CST  by NWS Corpus Christi</headline>
<description>...AREAS OF FOG THIS MORNING OVER VICTORIA CROSSROADS...
Areas of fog have developed across portions of the Victoria
Crossroads early this morning. Expect visibilities generally 1
mile or less with a few locations seeing visibilities 1/4 mile or
less at times through 8 AM.
Use caution if traveling as visibility may change rapidly
in a short amount of time. Use low beam headlights and leave
extra distance between your vehicle and others on the road.</description>
